Localization.Name: Keldur Hat and Indigo Goggles
Localization.Description: Blowing winds and blazing sun won't be an issue when wearing the Keldur hat and goggles. Insulated flaps keep the sun and elements off your neck, while a lightweight metal brim and scratch resistant, industrial-grade goggles protect your eyes.
